# 4-Node Local Vagrant test environment for Ansible using Virtualbox 

#If using Windows 10 with Hyper-v enabled , change image to Ubuntu 18.04 because ubuntu 20.04 has issues
using Virtualbox alongside Hyper-v using Ubuntu 20.04 https://forums.virtualbox.org/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=90853&start=270


#Step 1: Install Virtualbox
#Step 2: Install Vagrant
#Step 3: Git clone this repo and change CWD to the downloaded repos directory
#step 4: Vagrant up   
#step 5: vagrant ssh controller
#step 6: ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 2048
#step 7: ssh-copy-id node1      (repeat for node2 and node3 default user:vagrant default pw:vagrant)
